item.title: Gina Prince-Bythewood Set to Headline Film Independent’s Forum
item.description: Filmmaker Gina Prince-Bythewood is set to keynote the 2025 Film Independent Forum in a conversation moderated by Lena Waithe. The two-day forum will take place from Sept. 26-27 at the Directors Guild
